<p>有一种犬是带着使命和任务降生的，</p> 
<p>它们是警犬和军犬。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9260/926049edd8ab0404123e30c0ff47dae6.com/large/18aa0002eb7124d8fb41"></p> 
<p>经过严格的筛选，</p> 
<p>服从性好兴奋度强的幼犬会被选出进行训练</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9912/9912e521c69251cd0770abcf615664a7.com/large/18aa0002eb8a3447bf8e"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b70b/b70b7401e0361950766cf26c92390a9c.com/large/18aa0002eb955195d994"></p> 
<p>正和搭档一起跳下直升机的军犬。</p> 
<p>犬基本都怕高，</p> 
<p>但是为了任务为了配合主人，</p> 
<p>什么都可以克服！</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//32e0/32e05e973dea224fb283e86fdf3fe4ce.com/large/18ad0002ead97d110ff7"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6b89/6b899e2d983399006d546e67922bf729.com/large/1854000513ea9116021d"></p> 
<p>对军人来说，</p> 
<p>军犬不仅仅是一条犬，</p> 
<p>更是好战友。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//cb21/cb21897ed326f9a43b5004800f646492.com/large/184e00047acce5bb1f10"></p> 
<p>是可以互相把后背交给对方保护的好兄弟。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3452/34521f40cd1bce088ff50a1db8226137.com/large/18aa0002ebd6c96d7f4e"></p> 
<p>主人你好好休息，</p> 
<p>我来守护你！</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2b59/2b59d02d10786c901cbdd5737beb6b1c.com/large/18ab000252187c1f1e6b"></p> 
<p>执行任务的间隙，</p> 
<p>它们也特别需要照顾和疼爱。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//36c3/36c3a45420352c79a986f6ccab7b7a73.com/large/18aa0002ebe4201e8078"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//49b5/49b5dbf734e77c9a0274d7d86b413133.com/large/18b00002ec9996907c17"></p> 
<p>面对敌人凶神恶煞，</p> 
<p>面对主人温柔至极，</p> 
<p>谁还不是个宝宝！</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//e5d7/e5d70485a35ee4b0f5879e6dbcfcc6aa.com/large/18ad0002eb41db59bd72"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6178/6178327a6817202c79b5d78994c6f650.com/large/18ab0002523c38d870e1"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//56ec/56ec34354188280c1b45c8ffb62096b0.com/large/18ab0002523bcd2d1a58"></p> 
<p>一言不合就撒娇，</p> 
<p>满满的反差萌！</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//633d/633dd0e6297c32620542fc708fc149aa.com/large/18ac00002dab3217f2de"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3d5f/3d5f7286939216d5a5e53febb3adcfd7.com/large/18b00002ec98452ef2ef"></p> 
<p>在情势瞬息万变的战场上，</p> 
<p>难免有意外出现，</p> 
<p>但不管发生什么，</p> 
<p>汪都会坚定地信任你守护你。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//75fa/75fa02ec2a02e6a5531e923a43b0aed8.com/large/18540005145e794773f9"></p> 
<p>最不愿意看到的就是这种场景了，</p> 
<p>生离死别避无可避，</p> 
<p>但是汪还得振作起来，</p> 
<p>连着搭档的份，</p> 
<p>加倍努力完成任务！</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b0c1/b0c149cf1de1f7f195c537cd415b977f.com/large/184e00047b43ba25ea63"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8f89/8f895deb596717d253a3ad2377778a3b.com/large/18ac00002dc134cae5eb"></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//3463/3463a61013f46b7a091943b06f709469.com/large/18540005145c97168fc1"></p> 
<p>执行任务时并肩作战，</p> 
<p>日常生活中相互陪伴。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4550/455085c3e0376bce5dd1b326280556c9.com/large/18540005145d3947cb46"></p> 
<p>军犬警犬对于搭档来说，</p> 
<p>是一起出生入死，</p> 
<p>无条件信任的战友、兄弟！</p>狗 军事满满反差萌！威武的军犬警犬，原来私底下这么有爱！